DataDiction

IITK Consulting Group (ICG)

Project Introduction

Welcome to the DataDiction centralized data repository. This project aims to analyze the impact of smartphone usage on student lifestyle and academic performance. The dataset provided below contains standardized behavioral metrics collected across various demographics.

TASKS:

Scrape the table using BeautifulSoup library of Python

Convert the strings to int/float numeric using pandas

Train a NN on the given dataset
